 1-2-3 for Tandy Deskmate                     Nov. 1989
 1-2-3/M for IBM mainframes                   Feb. 1990
 1-2-3/G for OS/2 Presentation Manager       March 1990
 1-2-3 for Sun Microsystems                  March 1990
 1-2-3 for Digital Equipment VAX/VMS         April 1990
 1-2-3 for Systems V (Unix)                   June 1990
                                                                                                       

                                               DELIVERY
 UNDER DEVELOPMENT                           TIME FRAME
                                                                                                       

